        {
            "id": 6006403,
            "title": "〈焦點股〉油價回穩、5月營收公布前夕 台塑四寶堅挺上揚",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台塑 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1301:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1301\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1301-TW</a>) 四寶預計於下周一 (9 日) 公告 5 月業績說明與經營展望，加上油價波動趨緩、回穩，包括塑化相關原料現貨行情趨勢走穩，也讓今 (6) 日四寶股價盤中堅挺，以台化 (1326 -TW) 股價漲一度逾 4% 表現最為強勁，台塑化 (6505 -TW)、台塑漲逾 3%，南亞 (1303 -TW) 漲幅也超過 1.5%。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6006403%2Fl%2Fd97115584bc9f36a80a20e5c8184f497.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6006403%2Fl%2Fd97115584bc9f36a80a20e5c8184f497.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6006403%2Fl%2Fd97115584bc9f36a80a20e5c8184f497.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6006403%2Fl%2Fd97115584bc9f36a80a20e5c8184f497.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6006403%2Fl%2Fd97115584bc9f36a80a20e5c8184f497.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6006403%2Fl%2Fd97115584bc9f36a80a20e5c8184f497.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6006403%2Fl%2Fd97115584bc9f36a80a20e5c8184f497.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6006403%2Fl%2Fd97115584bc9f36a80a20e5c8184f497.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6006403%2Fl%2Fd97115584bc9f36a80a20e5c8184f497.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6006403%2Fl%2Fd97115584bc9f36a80a20e5c8184f497.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6006403%2Fl%2Fd97115584bc9f36a80a20e5c8184f497.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6006403%2Fl%2Fd97115584bc9f36a80a20e5c8184f497.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6006403%2Fl%2Fd97115584bc9f36a80a20e5c8184f497.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6006403%2Fl%2Fd97115584bc9f36a80a20e5c8184f497.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6006403%2Fl%2Fd97115584bc9f36a80a20e5c8184f497.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6006403%2Fl%2Fd97115584bc9f36a80a20e5c8184f497.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6006403%2Fl%2Fd97115584bc9f36a80a20e5c8184f497.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">油價回穩、5月營收發表前夕，台塑四寶盤中堅挺上揚。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台塑集團四大公司將在下周一公布 5 月合併營收並說明經營展望，隨著近日油價走穩，加上有塑化業者指出，油價下跌議題逐漸被消化掉，導致無論美國持續再增產，讓油價再下跌幅度有限，油價便宜也讓用量持穩增加，生產量能、消耗量會趨於平衡。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>分析師表示，塑化股低迷已久，但近期已持續進行轉型，尋求突破產業困境，以技術面觀察，目前台塑四寶，除了台塑化以外，其他三寶的目前股價高於淨值很多。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>分析師指出，觀察台塑集團族群股價的型態走勢，目前股價上方壓力都是年線為主，年線剛好都是在淨值附近，若股價持續往年線反彈，將是測試淨值的位置，股價有望向上反攻。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>法人表示，雖然近期原料乙、丙烯行情走勢疲軟，壓低石化產品價格，但第二季以往都是塑化傳統需求旺季，且美國對大陸以外國家，暫緩實施對等關稅 90 天，在廠商提前拉貨的預期下，將帶動塑化產品的需求增加。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
